headline: Apple, Ulta Beauty, AstraZeneca And A Real Estate Stock On CNBC's 'Final Trades'
summary: Joshua Brown is bullish on Apple Inc. Jim Lebenthal likes AstraZeneca PLC. Jenny Harrington says VICI Properties has high dividend yield. Joe Terranova names Ulta Beauty as final trade.
